Advantageously, the second set of transformation components includes:
a third transformer coupled to an output of the first transformer, wherein the third transformer outputs a first transmit signal to a first antenna;
a fourth transformer coupled to an output of the first transformer, wherein the fourth transformer outputs a second transmit signal to a second antenna;
a fifth transformer coupled to an output of the second transformer, wherein the fifth transformer outputs a third transmit signal to a third antenna; and
a sixth transformer coupled to an output of the second transformer, wherein the sixth transformer outputs a fourth transmit signal to a fourth antenna.

